etic diplomacy: two weeks of global exposure for the Korean team, particularly the women's hockey squad, which trained for weeks with North and South side by side getting along, taking selfies and learning about each other.\", \"from\": 3216, \"to\": 3478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3308, \"end\": 3314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9998393533717302, \"rank\": 0.0001606646213734509, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a strong dose\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3247}, {\"ngram\": \"athletic diplomacy\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3269}, {\"ngram\": \"two weeks\", \"from\": 3271, \"to\": 3280}, {\"ngram\": \"global exposure\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3299}, {\"ngram\": \"particularly the women's hockey squad\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3358}, {\"ngram\": \"weeks\", \"from\": 3378, \"to\": 3383}, {\"ngram\": \"North and South side\", \"from\": 3389, \"to\": 3409}, {\"ngram\": \"side\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3417}, {\"ngram\": \"selfies\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Sunday night, the closing ceremony will bookend those politics with U.S. President Donald Trump's daughter, Ivanka, in attendance as well as Kim Yong Chol, vice chairman of North Korea's ruling Workers' Party Central Committee and a man suspected of masterminding a lethal 2010 military attack on the South.\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3566, \"end\": 3578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999998481144, \"rank\": 1.5200215525458195e-10, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 3624, \"end\": 3627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_K